snippet.title: STINK EYE Trailer
snippet.description:
Chillyproof Games - Independent game makers based in Dublin. 
We invite you to save the world from  STINK EYE.
"Fun", "Fast", "Fantastical", "Frantic".
Be prepared for other "F" words...

Stink Eye is a free mobile game for Android available to download from the Google Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ChillyProof.Stinkeye
